judul: Juara 1 National Orienteering Sprint Celebes 1942 Jili VI MPA Alaska Fakultas Teknik Universitas Negeri Gorontalo
desk:
Mahasiswa Program Studi Akuntansi Sektor Publik, Fakultas Ekonomi dan Bisnis, Universitas Tadulako kini meraih Juara 1 National Orienteering Sprint Celebes 1942 Jili VI MPA Alaska Fakultas Teknik Universitas Negeri Gorontalo.
Congratulations to Rivaldi to your latest achievement as the 1st winner in National Orienteering Sprint Celebes 1942 Jili VI MPA Alaska Fakultas Teknik Universitas Negeri Gorontalo.
This is a great accomplishment and an invaluable opportunity to develop yourself.
